title: BENICIA 3/Bedroom 2/Bathroom, Southampton Single level Home
posting_body: ['Single Story Home located Southampton Road and Chelsea Hills:', '3 Bedroom, 2 bath, 2 car garage, "Bonus" Large Additional Family Room with vaulted ceiling.', 'Spacious bedrooms.', 'Formal living room with fireplace, open floor plan, kitchen, Master bedroom, carpet throughout home, laundry in garage w/d hookups.', 'Rear yard is private with room to roam.', ' Front and Back Yard (Patio) - Low maintenance.', ' Tenant pays all utilities, Access to Southampton Swimming Club.', ' Close to schools, shopping, restaurants and freeways Hwy 680/780/80.', '1 Year Lease', '$2,800 Monthly', 'Required: 1st Mo.', 'Rent $2,800 and Security Deposit $2,800.', 'NO Pets']
